description:
&quot;Snarked!&quot; is an original tale by Roger Langridge, broadly inspired by Lewis Carroll's oeuvre but freely drawing from and referencing literary classics by others just the same.

Originally published in 13 issues, pardon me, &quot;in 13 fits&quot;, I'd ordinarily have compiled what is a single contiguous story into a single volume. However, Empire's digital releases switched from lo-res to hi-res between &quot;Fit the Fourth&quot; and &quot;Fit the Fifth&quot;, which corresponds to a marked and somewhat natural partitioning of the series into &quot;books&quot;, which is why you get three of those instead, on this occasion.

